title: Air Force’s KC-46A Refueling Tanker Makes First Flight
text:
28 Air Force’s KC-46A Refueling Tanker Makes First Flight 
Defense Tech: The U.S. Air Force’s KC-46A refueling tanker made by Boeing Co. on Friday made its first flight in a historic milestone for the program that came after repeated delays.
